eya_def_tools.data_models.assessment_process_description.AssessmentProcessDescription
Description of a process used in an energy yield assessment.
Attributes: name (str): Name of the process or model use in the process. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.assessment_results.Result
Set of results for an element of an energy assessment.
Attributes: label (Optional[str]): Label of the results. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. assessment_period (AssessmentPeriod(StrEnum)): Period of or in time that has been assessed and for which the results are applicable. Default is 'lifetime'. dimensions (Optional[tuple[ResultsDimension(StrEnum), ...]]): Dimensions along which the results are binned (all result values in the same results object must have the same dimensions). Default is None. statistics (list[ResultStatistic]): List of result statistic objects that each include result values for a specific statistic type.

eya_def_tools.data_models.assessment_results.ResultStatistic
Result values for one specific statistic type.
Attributes: description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. statistic_type (StatisticType(StrEnum)): Type of statistic in the results component. values (UnionType[float, list[tuple[tuple[UnionType[float, int, str], ...], float]]]): Result as a single number or values at coordinates.

eya_def_tools.data_models.eya_def.EnergyAssessment
Energy assessment details and results.
Attributes: gross_eya_process (AssessmentProcessDescription): Specification of the model used to calculate the gross EYA estimates. gross_eya_results (list[Result]): Gross energy production predictions in GWh. plant_performance_loss_categories (list[PlantPerformanceCategory]): Plant performance loss assessment categories including results. net_energy_uncertainty_assessment (Optional[UncertaintyAssessment]): Net energy production uncertainty assessment, including the conversion of the wind resource assessment uncertainty results from wind speed to energy quantities and results for all main energy uncertainty categories. Default is None. net_eya_results (list[Result]): Net energy production predictions in GWh, including overall uncertainties and results at different confidence levels.

eya_def_tools.data_models.eya_def.PlantPerformanceCategory
Plant performance loss assessment category.
Attributes: label (PlantPerformanceCategoryLabel(StrEnum)): Label of the plant performance category. subcategories (list[PlantPerformanceSubcategory]): Plant performance assessment subcategories that fall under the category. category_results (list[Result]): Category level assessment results.

eya_def_tools.data_models.uncertainty.UncertaintyAssessment
Wind resource uncertainty assessment.
Attributes: categories (list[UncertaintyCategory]): List of wind resource uncertainty assessment categories.

eya_def_tools.data_models.eya_def.PlantPerformanceSubcategory
Plant performance loss assessment subcategory.
Attributes: label (PlantPerformanceSubcategoryLabel(StrEnum)): Label of the plant performance category. basis (AssessmentBasis(StrEnum)): Basis of plant performance element assessment. variability (VariabilityType(StrEnum)): Considered variability in plant performance element. assessment_processes (Optional[list[AssessmentProcessDescription]]): Calculation models used in the assessment. Default is None. results (Result): Plant performance assessment subcategory results.

eya_def_tools.data_models.uncertainty.UncertaintyCategory
Wind resource uncertainty assessment category.
Attributes: label (UncertaintyCategoryLabel(StrEnum)): Label of the uncertainty category. subcategories (list[UncertaintySubcategory]): Wind resource uncertainty assessment subcategories. category_results (list[Result]): Category level assessment results.

eya_def_tools.data_models.eya_def.Scenario
Single unique energy yield assessment scenario.
Attributes: scenario_id (Optional[str]): Unique identifier of the scenario. Default is None. label (str): Label of the scenario. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. is_main_scenario (Optional[bool]): Whether or not this is the main scenario in the report. Default is None. operational_lifetime_length_years (ConstrainedFloatValue): Number of years of project operational lifetime. wind_farms (list[WindFarmConfiguration]): List of all wind farms included in the scenario. wind_resource_assessment_reference (Optional[WindResourceAssessmentReference]): Measurement wind resource assessment reference for the scenario. Default is None. turbine_wind_resource_assessment (Optional[TurbineWindResourceAssessment]): Wind resource assessment at the turbine locations. Default is None. energy_assessment (EnergyAssessment): Energy assessment details and results, including gross energy, plant performance, net energy and uncertainties.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_farm.WindFarmConfiguration
A collection of wind turbines considered as one unit (plant).
Attributes: name (str): Name of the wind farm. label (Optional[str]): Abbreviated label of the wind farm. Default is None. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. turbines (list[TurbineConfiguration]): List of specifications for constituent turbines. relevance (WindFarmRelevance(StrEnum)): The relevance of the wind farm for the assessment. operational_lifetime_start_date (Optional[date]): Operational lifetime start date (format YYYY-MM-DD). Default is None. operational_lifetime_end_date (Optional[date]): Operational lifetime end date (format YYYY-MM-DD). Default is None. wind_farm_restrictions (Optional[list[OperationalRestriction]]): List of operational restrictions at the wind farm level. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_resource.TurbineWindResourceAssessment
Wind resource assessment at the turbine locations.
Attributes: turbine_wind_resource_results (list[Result]): Assessment results at the turbine location(s). wind_spatial_modelling_processes (list[AssessmentProcessDescription]): Wind spatial modelling processes used in the assessment. uncertainty_assessment (Optional[UncertaintyAssessment]): Turbine wind resource uncertainty assessment. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_resource.WindResourceAssessmentReference
Measurement wind resource assessment basis in a scenario.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_farm.OperationalRestriction
Specifications of a restriction that limits power output.
In the current draft of the schema, 'label', 'description' and 'comments' fields are available to describe the restriction with free text. This is intended to be expanded into a more comprehensive data model.
Attributes: label (str): Short label to indicate the type of operational restriction. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_farm.TurbineConfiguration
Specification of all details for a turbine configuration.
Attributes: turbine_id (Optional[str]): Unique identifier of the turbine specification. Default is None. label (str): Label of the turbine. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. location (Location): Horizontal location of the turbine. hub_height (float): Turbine hub height. turbine_model_id (str): Unique identifier of the turbine model. restrictions (Optional[list[OperationalRestriction]]): List of operational restrictions at the turbine level. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.spatial.Location
Specification of a horizontal location in space.
Attributes: location_id (Optional[str]): Unique identifier of the location. Default is None. label (Optional[str]): Label of the location. Default is None. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. x (float): Location x-coordinate (typically easing). y (float): Location y-coordinate (typically northing).

eya_def_tools.data_models.uncertainty.UncertaintySubcategory
Wind resource uncertainty assessment subcategory.
Attributes: label (str): Label of the wind resource uncertainty subcategory. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. results (list[Result]): Wind resource uncertainty assessment subcategory results.
